      "para_id": "Q001113.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Nanše of the E-engur ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001113.3",
      "line_range": "3",
      "translation": "(i 3) En-metena , ruler of Lagaš , chosen by Nanše in the heart , chief governor of Ninĝirsu , child of En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , built the E-engur in the field of Zulum for Nanše , decorated it for her with gold and silver , made it worthy of her , and embellished it for her with inscribed clay nails ."
    }
  ],
